title: DAZ3D - Michael 7 Pro Bundle TEMPLATES ONLY
description:
This bundle contains the template files for the Michael 7 Pro Bundle. 

Template files are not essential to use the bundle. They give a template from which it is possible to design your own textures for the characters or outfits in the bundle. Some people like to have the templates so I am including them here. 

Templates included:
Michael 7 Template
Fraser Hair Template
Mathew Hair Template
JustJosh template
M7 Intimates Template
Laid Back Outfit Template
Renegade for Genesis 3 Male Template
Swords of Time Template
Crimson Seas Template
